===Pokémon Evolutions===
Shauna appeared in ''[[PE03|The Visionary]]''. She and {{ga|Serena}} joined {{ga|Calem}} after he had defeated [[Lysandre]] at the [[Team Flare Secret HQ]]. When Lysandre started firing the [[ultimate weapon]], the three young Trainers fled the HQ together. Afterwards, they witnessed the weapon sinking back into the ground.
